summary: Learn about .SAH files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: SETI@home is a project that uses Internet-connected computers to download and analyze radio telescope data. Computer users voluntarily participate by donating computer idle time to scientific computation.

description: Data file used by SETI@home or other BOINC distributed computing applications; may define user information or work units for performing calculations on the local computer; used for configuring and storing data that is sent back to the SETI@home project.
